main event: Multiple UFO sightings reported in New Iberia, Louisiana during July 1964.
interesting points: Witnesses reported seeing a bright light traveling at high speed with a reddish-orange glow,The observation lasted approximately 30-45 seconds,Different witnesses described varying shapes of the objects such as disc-shaped and oval, An analysis concluded that some sightings were likely stars or planets, The reports were part of the U.S. Air Force's Project Blue Book.
sighted object: unidentified flying objects emitting bright lights
witness description: A teacher and two individuals who were outside at the time of the sightings.
